metadata.name: Tricolors beach
metadata.description:
Top down from a hidden beach in Menorca - Cala el Pilar.
It is a beach formed by gravel and golden sands. This dark reddish tone is characteristic of the north of Menorca.
Picture has been taken in October 2022. 
Camera: DJI Mini 3 Pro
Size: 2268 × 2835
